SAMSUNG FASCINATE APP MODS
==========================

BASE VERSION: EH03

REQUIRED TOOLS: apktool

FRAMEWORKS USED IN DECOMPILE (apktool -if <framework>):
    EH03 framework-res.apk (deodexed)
    EH03 twframework-res.apk (deodexed)

FRAMEWORK-RES.APK
=================

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d --keep-broken-res"
- Enable slow-blur effect from power button popup
- Enable CRT screen off animation (nitsuj17)
- Use EI20 edge glow PNGs
- Use EI20 battery graphics

SERVICES.JAR
============

- Changed default LiveWallpaper to com.android.wallpaper/.nexus.NexusWallpaper
- Increase default transition animation speed to "Fast"

AXT9IME.APK
===========

- Disabled key sound

BROWSER.APK
===========

- Removed all default bookmarks
- Set default home page to "about:blank"
- Set default search engine to Google
- Allow all bookmarks to be deleted and/or edited
- Fix Smart URL Filter so that all search engines function (google/yahoo/bing)

CAMERA.APK
==========

- Remap power button to trigger the shutter rather than locking the controls

CARCRADLE.APK
=============

- Modified View Map to launch Google Maps instead of Bing Maps
- Modified Voice Search to use Google Voice Search instead of Bing
- Modified Navigation to launch Google Maps instead of VZNavigator

DESKCRADLE.APK
==============

- Change voice search button to invoke Google Voice Search instead of Bing

DIALERTABACTIVITY.APK
=====================

- Modified voicemail button to dial voicemail instead of VZW Visual Voice Mail

JOBMANAGER.APK
==============

- Don't hide Google Maps, Magic Smoke Live Wallpaper or Dual Clock widget from Task Manager
- Hide many well-known launchers from Task Manager

MUSICPLAYER.APK
===============

- Localize some strings for US English
- Remove "Download from V cast?" prompt when no media exists

SYSTEMUI.APK
============

- NOTE: Was decompiled with "apktool d -r" due to problem linking back to twframework-res.apk
- Remove full battery notification

TOUCHWIZ30LAUNCHER.APK
======================

- Modified default application list order to match my ROM
- Modified default shortcut and widget layouts
 

